# SLURM job output / accounting
# Job IDs are non-deterministic and these files are stdout dumps; the
# canonical run state lives in output/<run_tag>/run_config.json sidecars
# (git_hash, git_dirty, resolved weights, per-file metric hashes). If a
# specific slurm-out is needed for a post-mortem, copy it INTO the
# corresponding output/<run_tag>/ directory rather than committing at root.
slurm-*.out
slurm-*.err

